-- Ford says H1 China retail vehicle sales up 25 pct
-- 
-- Thu Jul 5, 2007 4:14am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/07/05/us-ford-china-sales-idUSSHA28074020070705

 

 SHANGHAI  (Reuters) - Ford Motor Co. ( F.N ) said on Thursday its China retail vehicle sales rose 25 percent year-on-year in the first half to 93,206 units. 

 "Adding to the momentum of fast growth in 2006, Ford Motor Company in China continued to post a vigorous retail sales result for the first half of 2007," the company's China unit said in a statement.